channel.title: Santa's Gift Tracking Service Port Mystery :: SANS Holiday Hack Challenge 2025
channel.description: Objective Difficulty: 1/5 Chat with Yori near the apartment building about Santa’s mysterious gift tracker and unravel the holiday mystery. Yori Kvitchko mission statement Hi! I’m Yori. I was Ed’s lost intern back in 2015, but I was found! Think you can check out this terminal for me? I need to use cURL to access the gift tracker system, but it has me stumped.
